The Full Page Prompt is a fullscreen, dialog-like prompt shown centered on the page.
It is meant for cases where we need to interrupt the normal workflow and focus the user on a single decision.

## Overview

<%= embed OpPrimer::FullPagePromptComponentPreview, :default, panels: %i[source] %>

## Anatomy

The component is composed of:

- **Icon** (optional)
- **Title** (required)
- **Content** (required)
- **Primary action** (required)

